<subSubSection pageId="55" pageNumber="763" type="breeding">
<paragraph blockId="55.[100,1306,719,1378]" pageId="55" pageNumber="763">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[102,235,837,866]" pageId="55" pageNumber="763">Breeding.</emphasis>
Gestation of the Whiskered Flying Squirrel is ¢.53 days, and females give birth to one precocial young.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[100,931,917,946]" pageId="55" pageNumber="763" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="55.[100,1306,719,1378]" box="[100,931,917,946]" pageId="55" pageNumber="763">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[100,335,917,946]" pageId="55" pageNumber="763">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
